<plot>Thou Art That has elements of role reversal and the alter ego. The film attempts to show that we are what we observe. The main character vicariously lives through his dream state where he is able to victimize and take command. The person who victimizes becomes the victim.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?605409</url></doc>
